flowchart TB
    GW[API Gateway]

    BFF[BFF Layer<br/>Journey-Level]

    ORCH[Journey Orchestrator<br/>Workflow Control]

    MS[Business Microservices]

    CACHE[Redis Cache<br/>TLS]
    DB[(RDS / NoSQL / Vector DB)]
    DOC[S3 / Document Store]
    EVT[Event Platform]

    AI[AI Orchestrator]
    GEN[GenAI / LLM]

    INT[Integration Layer<br/>External Systems]

    MON[Monitoring / SIEM]
    SEC[Secrets / KMS / IAM]

    GW -->|JWT + Rate Limit| BFF

    BFF --> |JWT Validation|ORCH
    BFF --> |Workflow Control|MS
    BFF --> |TLS|CACHE

    ORCH --> |Service-Level JWT|MS

    MS --> |Secure DB protocol|DB
    MS --> |Service-Level JWT + RBAC + ABAC|DOC
    MS --> |Kafka / AMQP + TLS/mTLS|EVT
    MS --> |OAuth2 / API Keys|INT

    BFF --> |JWT Validation|AI
    AI --> |Policy + JWT|GEN
    AI --> |Secure DB protocol|DB

    SEC --- |HTTPS|BFF
    SEC --- |HTTPS|MS
    SEC --- |HTTPS|DB

    MS --> MON
    ORCH --> MON
    AI --> MON